main event: A UFO sighting was reported in Kettering, Ohio on April 1, 1954.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for 5 minutes,The object observed was possibly mistaken for an aircraft but later concluded not to be one,There were no photographs present despite claims in the document,The object was described as whitish and possibly spherical or oval-shaped,The object was observed to have moved in a northeastern direction.
sighted object: a whitish spherical or oval-shaped object
